  <h2>CLI Usage</h2>
  <p>You can also use AXON from the command line:</p>

  <pre><code># Convert JSON to AXON
axon encode data.json -o data.axon

# See token savings
axon stats data.json data.axon

# Convert back to JSON
axon decode data.axon -o output.json</code></pre>

